{
  "stem": "24137.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the two other children, the little boy and the little girl, they got sick with tuberculosis.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I remember we were lying there on the floor, in these barracks, a lot, a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] A lot of crying, and a lot of sighing, and a lot of, kind of, going to die.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I still remember people being taken to die, and I remember people just dying from hunger.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I remember one day, the trucks came, and they said they're taking all the sick people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I took my cousins, and we went under the barrack.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The barrack was standing on stilts.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there was-- there was some kind of a sand or earth or something, and we all pushed ourselves into that, under the barracks, because we were all so scared of these trucks.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I remember we waited, and we waited, and we waited, and we probably fainted, because I don't remember what happened for a very long time.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But then I remember, when we did open our eyes, we got out from this sand or whatever it was, and we went up into the barrack, and my aunt wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They took her away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And it was now just us, the four children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And now, we were just so sick that we could not even function.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we were getting this bread.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I suppose it was towards the end of the war, and many Nazis were already fleeing themselves, and there weren't that many trucks.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So they couldn't take so many people to kill them, wherever they were taking them.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
